      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WICKED WIZARD (4) made a nice return at his latest appearance a week ago, finishing 1.4 metres away in second at Bendigo. That was his first outing since a fourth at Listed level here in December and he will be fitter for it. Can progress and win. CHRISSY EVE (9) produced a good effort last time when she came from this barrier for second at this venue, finishing just 1.6 metres from the winner. Should enjoy a soft run from this draw and the sprint lane is in play. Go well again. BULLETIN (7) draws wide but hasn't done a bad job in two starts so far this campaign and has won when third-up before. ELLENS DELIGHT (2) draws well again and is in the mix after turning in a good effort last start to finish third at this venue.",
